  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Sisma L4 is a compact, high-output LED wash beam moving head offering an extremely wide zoom range that quickly transforms from a narrow beam of light for dramatic aerial effects to a flood of evenly distributed light with saturated, vibrant colors. Sisma L4 integrates 7 x 60W RGBL LED chips that deliver upgraded CRI with expanded color mixing, refined color temperature control, and increased white light output. It integrates an ultra-wide zoom range as low as 2.5deg for tight long-throwing beams, to an ultra-wide 60º soft wash. All while maintaining a lightweight, compact form factor complemented by precise, ultra-fast pan/tilt movements. Its advanced color control can offer, precision-based concentrated colors without compromising brightness. Sisma is the ultimate dually-capable fixture for dynamic lighting effects that can raise the bar for creative design.",
